Project Structure File
-----------------------
I am using Python, pytest, and pytest-bdd in PyCharm and set to structure the automation portion using:

1. Gherkin feature files for scenarios.

2. Step definitions using pytest-bdd.

3. Requests library for API calls.

4. Assertions and maybe time or datetime for checks like response time and date comparisons.



bbc_test_assessment/
│
├── features_including_manual_tests/
│   ├── scenario_1.feature
│   ├── scenario_2.feature
│   └── ...
│
├── steps_including_test_api_steps/
│   ├── test_scenario_1_steps.py
│   ├── test_scenario_2_steps.py
│   └── ...
│
├── conftest.py
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md


